  <div>
    <h2>Pattern Naming convention:</h2>
    <h3>Pattern variables:</h3>
    <p>Pattern variables are not prefixed. To configure sub elements use "__". E.g:
      "subcomponentname__variable_name" </p>
    <p><code><span>{</span>% set headline__element = headline__element|default('h2') %<span>}</span></code></p>
    <h3>SASS variables for components:</h3>
    <p>See <a href="http://getbem.com/introduction">BEM documentation</a></p>
    <p><code>$tape__fonts: (c-green: #b8d096, c-beige: #e7c689);</code></p>
    <h3>Components structure</h3>
    <h4>Classes: </h4>
    <p><code><span>{</span># Classes: <span>#</span>}<br>
        <span>{</span>% set classes = classes|default([])|merge([<br>
        &nbsp;&nbsp;'teaser',<br>
        &nbsp;&nbsp;text_alignment,<br>
        ]) | sort | join(' ') | trim %<span>}</span></code></p>
    <p>Define here the base class of the component and all possible modifiers. </p>
    <h4>Defaults: </h4>
    <p><code><span>{</span># Defaults: <span>#</span>}<br>
        <span>{</span>% set element = element|default('div') %<span>}</span></code></p>
    <p>Define here the default behavior of your component. For example the base tag etc.</p>
    <h4>Define your component:</h4>
    <p>The markup of your component.</p>
